================================= Queries ====================================

1. Create Database 
	Syntax:	create database databaseName;

2. Use Database
	Syntax:	use databaseName;

3. Create Table :
	Syntax: 
	create table tableName (colName datatype (size) , ......);

	Basic Data Type 
	int
	decimal
	date
	varchar


